cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves computer vision techniques for extracting visual features and machine learning algorithms for training an editing controller. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves multimedia processing, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of machine learning algorithms for training the editing controller suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence techniques for automatic video editing, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper may also belong to cs.GR (Graphics) as it involves cinematography editing rules.
